\id 2CO - Indian Revised Version (IRV) Nagamese
\h 2 Corinthians
\toc1 Corinth Logot Paul He Likha Duitio Chithi
\toc2 2 Corinthians
\toc3 2 Co
\mt1 Corinth Logot Paul He Likha Duitio Chithi
\c 1
\s1 Salam Kotha
\p 
\v 1 Paul\f + \fr 1.1 \ft Etu chithi bhi Paul ekela pora likhise. Kintu Paul pora Timothy laga salam bhi janai di ase.\f*, jun Isor laga itcha pora Khrista Jisu laga apostle ase, aru amikhan laga bhai Timothy, Corinth sheher te thaka Isor laga girja ke, aru Achaia jagate thaka sob pobitro jonke.
\v 2 Anugrah aru shanti Isor amikhan laga Baba aru Probhu Jisu Khrista pora aha apnikhan logote thaki bole dibi.
\s1 Sob Te Anondo Diya Isor
\p 
\v 3 Asis hobi Isor aru amikhan laga Probhu Jisu Khrista laga Baba, jun daya laga Baba ase aru mon aram diya laga Baba ase,
\v 4 Kun pora amikhan laga sob dukh te anondo kori diye, titia amikhan pora bhi dusra khan ke anondo dibole paribo, etu eke anondo Isor pora amikhan ke bhi anondo dise.
\v 5 Kilekoile kineka Khrista laga dukh te amikhan bhi bhag hoi ase, thik etu nisena, Khrista te amikhan bhi bisi anondo pai ase.
\v 6 Kintu jodi amikhan digdar pai ase, etu apnikhan laga anondo aru poritran nimite ase, jodi amikhan anondo pai ase, etu to apnikhan ke anondo dibo nimite ase, aru etu pora apnikhan bhi nomro kori kene amikhan laga dukh te bhag hobo.
\v 7 Aru amikhan laga asha apnikhan nimite thaka to mojbut ase, amikhan laga dukh te apnikhan bhi bhag ase koi kene jani ase, etu nisena anondo te bhi bhag ase.
\v 8 Kilekoile bhai khan, amikhan uporte Asia\f + \fr 1.8 \ft Asia to Rome pora raj kora jaga asele aru ta te Ephesus he sob pora bisi dangor sheher thakise. \f* jagate ki digdar hoise, etu apnikhan najani kene thakibo dibo mon nai. Ta te amikhan dukh pa to amikhan laga takot bahar thakise aru etu nimite amikhan jinda thaki bole bhi asha nathaka hoi jaisele.
\v 9 Hosa pora bhi, amikhan morai dibole hukum thakisele, eneka hoile he amikhan nijor uporte nohoi kene, Isor kun pora mora ke jinda kori diye, Tai uporte biswas thakibo nimite.
\v 10 Isor he amikhan ke mori bole thaka pora bachai dise, aru Tai amikhan ke aru bhi bachai lobo. Tai uporte amikhan laga asha to rakhidise titia Tai amikhan ke bachai thakibo,
\v 11 apnikhan bhi eke logote mili kene amikhan nimite prathana koribi, titia amikhan uporte bisi manu pora modot kora nimite apnikhan ke bisi manu khan dhanyavad dibo.
\s1 Paul Laga Bhabona Bodli Kora
\p 
\v 12 Kilekoile etu nimite amikhan mon dangor kore: aru amikhan laga thik bhabona pora etu gawahi di ase, amikhan ji kaam etu prithibi te korise, etu pobitro aru hosa mon pora korise, aru mangso laga buddhi pora nohoi, kintu Isor laga kripa pora, aru asol to apuni khan logot te he kaam to bisi korise.
\v 13 Kilekoile amikhan dusra eku bhi likha nai, khali juntu apnikhan puribole aru bujhi bole pare. Kintu etiya ami asha ase apuni khan pura bujhi jabo,
\v 14 jineka apuni khan age pora amikhan laga bisi kotha bujhi kene ase, titia apnikhan bhi Probhu Jisu wapas aha laga dinte amikhan nimite mon dangor dikha bo, aru amikhan bhi apuni khan nimite dikha bo.
\p 
\v 15 Aru mon dangor pora, moi age te apnikhan logote ahibole bhabona korise, titia apnikhan aru dusra bar asirbad pabo,
\v 16 aru Macedonia jagate jai thaka homoi te apnikhan ke paar kori kene jabo, aru Macedonia pora wapas aha homoi te bhi, aru ami Judea jagate jabole nimite apnikhan pora amike modot koribo.
\v 17 Etu karone, jitia ami eneka pora bhabona kori thakise, moi etu ke asani pora luwa nai, na loise? Na ami ki bhabona korise etu to mangso laga itcha pora he hoise, juntu nimite apnikhan eke somoite “Hoi, hoi” aru “Nohoi, nohoi” eneka koi ase?
\v 18 Kintu Isor to hosa ase, etu nimite amikhan laga kotha apnikhan ke khali “Hoi” aru “Nohoi” eneka hobo napare.
\v 19 Kilekoile Isor laga Putro, Jisu Khrista, junke ami aru Silvanus aru Timothy pora apnikhan majote prochar kori dise- Tai to “Hoi” aru “Nohoi” thaka nai, kintu khali “Hoi” he thakise.
\v 20 Kilekoile Tai bhitor te, Isor laga sob vachan khan “Hoi” ase. Etu nisena Tai dwara amikhan pora “Amen” koi ase, Tai laga mohima nimite.
\v 21 Etiya Isor he ekjon ase jun pora ami aru apnikhan ke Khrista te takot bonai dise, aru Tai laga kaam nimite amikhan ke basi loise,
\v 22 Tai pora amikhan ke Tai nimite mohor lagai dise, aru Atma laga kosom amikhan laga monte dise.
\p 
\v 23 Moi hosa pora koi ase, Isor ke ami laga gawah hobo nimite mati ase, moi apnikhan ke saja nadibo karone Corinth te aha nai.
\v 24 Amikhan eneka kora to apuni khan laga biswas ke amikhan laga nichete rakhi kene chola bo nimite nohoi, kintu, amikhan sob apnikhan logote mili kene kaam kora manu khan ase aru apnikhan laga khushi nimite ase, kele koile apnikhan laga biswas to bisi mojbut hoi kene ase.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Moi laga mon nijor pora etu bhabi loise, moi apnikhan logote mon dukh hoi kene aru nahibo.
\v 2 Kilekoile jodi moi apnikhan ke mon dukh kori diye, tinehoile kun pora amike mon khushi kori dibo, ami pora mon biya kori diya khan pora nohoile?
\v 3 Aru moi etu eke kotha khan likhi ase, eneka hoile jitia moi ahibo, moi jun khan uporte moi laga mon khushi thakibo lage, taikhan pora moi laga mon dukh nakoribo karone, aru moi apnikhan sobke pura mon pora biswas ase ami laga khushi to apnikhan sob laga khushi hobo koi kene\f + \fr 2.3 \ft Paul to Corinthia girja ke tinta chithi likhise. Kintu ekta to haraise. Yate Paul etu koi ase.\f*.
\v 4 Kilekoile moi laga mon bisi bikhai kene aru dukh hoi kene likhi ase, suku pani giri kene, kintu apnikhan ke mon dukh kori dibo nimite nohoi, hoilebi ami laga morom apnikhan nimite bisi thaka to janai dibo nimite ase.
\s1 Paapi khan Ke Khyama Dibi
\p 
\v 5 Jodi kunba pora mon dukh kori bole dise, tai moi ekla ke mon dukh kori diya nohoi, hoile bhi, olop kori kene- moi laga kotha kara nalagaibo nimite- apnikhan sob laga mon dukh koridi ase\f + \fr 2.5 \ft Gal. 4:12.\f*.
\v 6 Eneka ekjon manu nimite etu sajai he thik ase, manu bisi pora taike golti diya to he kafi ase,
\v 7 etu hoile ulta apnikhan taike maph kori dibole lage, aru tai laga mon dangor kori dibole lage. Tinehoile, eneka ekjon ke bisi mon dukh pora khai dibo\f + \fr 2.7 \ft Eph. 4:32. \f*.
\v 8 Eneka nimite, ami apnikhan ke utsah kori ase, apnikhan laga morom tai phale thik pora rakhibi.
\v 9 Kilekoile etiya bhi ami apuni khan ke likhi ase, tinehoile ami apuni khan ke porikha kori bole paribo, apuni khan sob phale kotha mani kene ase na nai.
\v 10 Junke apnikhan jineka pora hoile bhi maph kori dise, ami bhi maph koridi ase- kele koile ami kunba ke maph korise -junke ami maph koridi ase-, ami apnikhan nimite Khrista bhitor te thaka manu hoi kene maph koridi ase,
\v 11 eneka nohoile Saitan amikhan pora labh uthabo. Kilekoile amikhan tai laga chalak khan najani kene thaka nohoi.
\s1 Khrista Te Jiti Luwa
\p 
\v 12 Jitia ami Khrista laga susamachar laga kotha jonai dibole nimite Troas te ahisele, ami usorte Probhu laga ekta dorja khuli sele.
\v 13 Ami laga atma bhitor te aram thaka nai, kele koile ami laga bhai Titus\f + \fr 2.13 \ft Timothy nisena Titus bhi Paul logot Isor laga kaam kora ekjon asele.\f* ke ami bisarikena paa nai. Etu pora, ami taikhan ke chari kene Macedonia te jai jaise.
\p 
\v 14 Etiya Isor ke dhanyavad ase, jun amikhan ke hodai Khrista dwara jiti bole di thake, aru amikhan dwara pora tel laga mitha sugandh laga gyaan sob jagate dikhai thake.
\v 15 Kilekoile amikhan Isor usorte Khrista laga mitha sugandh thaka ase, taikhan nimite jun khan ke bachai loi ase, aru taikhan jun khan harai ase-
\v 16 Jun khan harai ase taikhan nimite amikhan mora laga gundh ase, aru jun khan ke bachi loi ase taikhan nimite jibon laga sugandh ase. Aru kun eitu khan pabole thik ase?
\v 17 Kilekoile amikhan bisi jon nisena nohoi, jun khan Isor laga kotha ke bisi halka pora cholai ase, hoile bhi amikhan to hosa pora Isor usorte amikhan Khrista bhitor te thaki kene koi ase.
\c 3
\s1 Notun Niom Laga Sewak
\p 
\v 1 Amikhan aru bhi nijorke untcha kori bole shuru hoi ase? Amikhan to bhal naam laga chithi apnikhan pora nohoile bhi amikhan nimite lagi ase naki, dusra manu khan dorkar kora nisena?
\v 2 Apnikhan he amikhan laga mon bhitor te likhi kene thaka chithi ase, sob manu khan pora jani ase aru puri ase,
\v 3 apnikhan Khrista laga chithi ase koi kene dikhai dise, junke amikhan pora sai dise, kolom pora likhi kene nohoi, kintu jinda Isor laga Atma pora, pathor laga tukrate nohoi, hoile bhi mon laga tukrate\f + \fr 3.3 \ft Exo. 24:12, Jer. 31:33, Eze. 11:19-20. \f*.
\v 4 Aru Khrista dwara amikhan Isor phale eneka biswas ase.
\v 5 Amikhan sob parikena sob to amikhan pora he kori ase eneka kobole nohoi. Hoile bhi Isor he amikhan ke paribole di ase,
\v 6 Jun pora amikhan ke notun vachan nimite yogya hobole dise; likha kotha pora nohoi, hoilebi Atma pora hoise. Kilekoile likhi kene thaka kotha\f + \fr 3.6 \ft Likhi kene rakha Yehudi Niom khan koi ase.\f* to mori bole diye, hoilebi Pobitro Atma pora he jibon diye\f + \fr 3.6 \ft Exo. 24:8, Jer. 31:31, 32:40. \f*.
\v 7 Hoilebi juntu porisorja pora mrityu anise- juntu pathor khan te khundi kene likhise- iman mohima te ahise, juntu nimite Israel laga bacha khan Moses laga mukh phine sabole para nai, kele koile tai mukh laga mohima to komti hoi asele,
\v 8 tinehoile, kineka Pobitro Atma laga kaam khan etu pora bhi bisi mohima thaka nahobo?
\v 9 Kilekoile jodi bodnam kori diya laga kaam khan te mohima thakise koile, dhormikta laga kaam khan to mohima pora bhorta hobo!
\v 10 Kilekoile juntu mohima ase koi thakise, etiya utu hisab te mohima nai, kele koile etiya laga mohima to he bisi dangor ase\f + \fr 3.10 \ft Exo. 34:29-30. \f*.
\v 11 Kilekoile juntu khotom hoijai ase utu laga mohima pora ahise koile, juntu thaki ase etu to aru bhi kiman bisi dangor mohima pora ahibo!
\p 
\v 12 Tinehoile jitia dikhi ase amikhan laga eneka asha ase, amikhan mon dangor huwa kotha koi thake,
\v 13 Aru Moses nisena nohoi, jun tai laga mukh uporte ekta kapra rakhise, eneka pora Isor laga bacha khan utu laga piche phine saikene nathakibo juntu khotom hoijai ase\f + \fr 3.13 \ft Exo. 34:33,35.\f*.
\v 14 Hoilebi Israel manu khan to taikhan laga bhabona ke bon kori kene rakhise. Kilekoile aji tak bhi purana niyom khan pura homoi te utu kapra ke nahataikena rakhi ase. Utu kapra ke uthai diya nai, kele koile Khrista dwara he etu khotom hoijai ase.
\v 15 Hoilebi aji tak bhi, jitia Moses ke porhe\f + \fr 3.15 \ft Moses ke diya Isor laga Niom.\f*, utu kapra taikhan laga mon uporte ase.
\v 16 Eneka hoile bhi jitia ekjon Probhu phale ahibo, utu kapra ke hatai diye\f + \fr 3.16 \ft Exo. 34:34, Isa. 25:7.\f*.
\v 17 Etiya Probhu Atma ase: aru jun jagate Probhu laga Atma ase, ta te ajadi ase.
\v 18 Hoilebi amikhan sob, mukh te eku bhi nalagaikena sisate sa-a nisena Probhu laga mohima sai ase, aru nijor bhi eneka pora mohima paikena bodli hoi ase, jineka Probhu laga Atma pora hoi ase.
\c 4
\s1 Susamachar Laga Puhor
\p 
\v 1 Etu karone, etu porisorja kaam kori thaka to, jineka amikhan Isor laga daya paise, amikhan mon chutu nohoi.
\v 2 Hoile bhi lukai kene thaka misa khan chari dise, chalak kori kene na berabo, Isor laga kotha thoga baji nimite nacholabo; hoilebi hosa ke dikhai kene Isor usorte sob manu laga mon laga bhabona te nijorke thik korise.
\v 3 Hoilebi jodi amikhan prochar kora susamachar to dhaki kene ase, etu taikhan nimite ase jun khan harai kene ase,
\v 4 jun khan bhitor te etu yug laga isor\f + \fr 4.4 \ft ‘Yug laga isor’ to saitan ke koi ase.\f* pora abiswasi khan laga dimag ke bondh kori dise, eneka pora Khrista laga mohima laga susamachar, jun Isor nisena ase, taikhan uporte pohor nathake.
\v 5 Kilekoile amikhan nije ke prochar kora nohoi, kintu Probhu Jisu Khrista ke; aru amikhan nijor apnikhan laga noukar ase, Jisu nimite.
\v 6 Kilekoile Isor he ase, jun koise, “Andhar pora puhor to ujala ulai ahibo,” jun amikhan laga mon bhitor te ujala korise, Isor laga mohima laga gyaan laga puhor Jisu Khrista laga chehera pora dikha bole nimite\f + \fr 4.6 \ft Isa. 9:2.\f*.
\s1 Mati Laga Kolsi Te Dhun
\p 
\v 7 Hoilebi amikhan logote etu khajana to mati kolsi\f + \fr 4.7 \ft Mati pora bona dekchi borton khan. Yate etu borton to manu laga gaw mangso ke koi ase.\f* khan bhitor te ase, tinehoile etu iman dangor takot to Isor laga he hobo, aru amikhan laga nohoi.
\v 8 Amikhan sob phale digdar ase, eneka hoile bhi mon dukh nai; amikhan ulta-pulta hoi kene ase, hoile bhi bhabona harai kene thaka nohoi.
\v 9 Biswas nimite dukh kosto paise, kintu amikhan ke chari diya nohoi. Amikhan ke mari kene girai dise, hoile bhi khotom kori diya nohoi.
\v 10 Hodai Probhu Jisu laga mora gaw ke bukhi kene thaki ase, titia Jisu laga jibon bhi amikhan laga gaw te dikhi bole pabo.
\v 11 Kilekoile amikhan jun khan jinda ase Jisu nimite hodai mori bole nisena hoijai, titia amikhan laga mori bole thaka gaw te Jisu laga jibon bhi dikhi bole pabo.
\v 12 Etu nimite mrityu to amikhan bhitor te kaam kori ase, hoilebi jibon to apnikhan bhitor te ase.
\v 13 Amikhan logote eke biswas laga atma ase, likhi kene thaka nisena, “Ami biswas korise; aru etu nimite ami kotha koise. Amikhan bhi biswas korise aru etu nimite amikhan bhi koise\f + \fr 4.13 \ft Psa. 116:10.\f*,
\v 14 amikhan jani ase tai jun Probhu Jisu ke uthaise, amikhan ke bhi Jisu logote uthabo, aru amikhanke aru apnikhan ke eke logote Tai usorte loijabo.
\v 15 Kilekoile eitu khan sob apnikhan nimite ase, tinehoile kiman dangor anugraha sob phale jai ase, tineka he Isor laga mohima nimite dhanyavad bisi diya he hobo.
\p 
\v 16 Etu nimite amikhan alsi hoi najai. Amikhan laga gaw mangso to bura hoijai ase, hoilebi, amikhan laga bhitor laga atma to din-dinte notun koridi ase.
\v 17 Kilekoile amikhan laga olop dukh khan, juntu olop homoi nimite he ase, amikhan nimite bisi bhal aru kitia bhi khotom nahobole bisi dangor nimite kaam kori ase.
\v 18 Amikhan utu jinis khan ke sa-a nohoi juntu dikhi ase, hoilebi utu jinis khan ke sai ase juntu dikhi bole napare. Kilekoile ki dikhi ase, etu olop homoi nimite he ase; hoile ki suku pora nadikhe, etu he anonto ase.
\c 5
\s1 Sorgote Amikhan Laga Jaga
\p 
\v 1 Kilekoile amikhan jani ase jodi amikhan prithibi te thaka tombu laga ghor\f + \fr 5.1 \ft Prithibi laga tombu ghor laga motlob ase amikhan laga gaw, juntu ekta tombu nisena ase. Jitia manu moribo, titia itu tombu ghor to bhangi jai. Etu hisab te, Paul to mora laga kotha kuwa ase.\f* to bhangi jaise koile bhi, amikhan logote Isor laga ghor ase, juntu hath pora bona nohoi, hoilebi sorgo khan te thaka anonto ghor ase\f + \fr 5.1 \ft Heb. 9:11, Job 4:19. \f*.
\v 2 Kilekoile etu tombu laga ghor te amikhan dukh pora hala kori ase, aru amikhan ke sorgo laga kapra lagai dibole itcha ase,
\v 3 Eneka pora amikhan ke kapra lagai dise koile amikhan ke kapra nalagai kene napabo\f + \fr 5.3 \ft Etu laga motlob ase amikhan thaki bole ghor nathaka nohobo.\f*.
\v 4 Kilekoile amikhan jun khan etu tombu laga ghor te ase dukh paikena hala kori ase, bisi bhari ujon bukhi kene, kelemane amikhan kapra nalagaikena thaka hobo mon nai, kintu kapra lagai kene thakibo mon ase, titia mori bole thaka gaw ke jibon pora khai dibo.
\v 5 Etiya tai jun amikhanke eneka kori bole dise etu Isor ase, jun amikhan ke Atma bisari bole nimite ekta bhabona bhi dise.
\v 6 Etu nimite amikhan hodai mon-dangor kori kene ase, etu janikena, jiman tak amikhan etu ghor te thaki kene gaw bhitor te ase, amikhan utu Probhu logote nai-
\v 7 Kilekoile amikhan biswas pora berai ase, dikhi kene nohoi-
\v 8 Amikhan mon dangor ase, aru bhabi ase etu gaw te nathaki jabo, aru Probhu logote he thakibo.
\v 9 Etu nimite amikhan kaam kori ase, titia, thakile bhi nohoile nathakile bhi, amikhan ke Tai khushi pabo.
\v 10 Kilekoile amikhan sob Khrista bisar kora laga singhason age te khara hobole lagibo, tinehoile sob manu pabo juntu tai nijor gaw te korise, jineka tai korise, bhal hoilebi biya hoilebi\f + \fr 5.10 \ft Eph. 6:8, Mat. 16:27, Ecc. 12:14. \f*.
\s1 Mil-milap Kora Kaam
\p 
\v 11 Etu nimite Probhu laga bhoi janikena, amikhan pora manu khan ke kotha mani bole koi ase. Kintu amikhanke Isor pora dikhai dise, aru ami etu bhi asha kori ase apuni khan laga mon laga bhabona te amikhan ke bujhi di ase.
\v 12 Kilekoile apnikhan usorte aru bhi bhal hobole nimite eneka kora nohoi, hoile bhi apuni khan pora amikhan nimite phutani kori bole ekta homoi di ase, titia apnikhan taikhan ke jowab dibole paribo jun khan khali bahar te he sai, aru mon-bhitor nohoi.
\v 13 Kilekoile amikhan pagala hoile, etu Isor logote ase: nohoile amikhan dimag thaka hoile, etu to apnikhan nimite ase.
\v 14 Kilekoile Khrista laga morom pora amikhanke eneka kori bole joborjosti kori ase, kele koile amikhan eneka jani loise: ekjon manu\f + \fr 5.14 \ft Ekjon manu to Khrista ase.\f* pora sob nimite morise; etu karone sob manu morise.
\v 15 Aru kele koile Tai sob nimite morise, titia kunkhan jinda ase etiya pora nijor nimite jinda nathakibo, hoilebi Jun taikhan nimite morise, aru bhi uthise Tai nimite he jinda thakibo.
\v 16 Etu nimite, etiya pora amikhan mangso hisab te manu ke nasabo. Hoi, amikhan Khrista ke mangso hisab te janise, hoilebi etiya to amikhan Taike eneka pora nasai.
\v 17 Etu nimite, kunba manu Khrista bhitor te ase koile, tai ekjon notun bonai luwa jon hoise. Purana khan paar hoise. Sabi, etiya sob to notun hoise\f + \fr 5.17 \ft Isa. 43:18-19.\f*.
\v 18 Aru etu sob Isor laga ase, jun nije ke Jisu Khrista dwara amikhan logote milai loise, aru amikhan ke mil-milap kori dibole laga kaam dise.
\v 19 Etu bujhai diya kotha to eneka ase, Khrista dwara Isor pora prithibi ke nijor logote milai loise, aru eku golti khan taikhan usorte rakha nai; aru amikhanke etu prithibi te mil-milap kori bole laga kaam to dise.
\p 
\v 20 Etiya tinehoile amikhan Khrista laga janai diya manu khan ase, jineka Isor amikhan ke cholai kene apuni khan ke morom pora koi ase. Amikhan Khrista laga naam te apuni khan logote prathana kori ase, apuni khan “Isor logote milai lobi\f + \fr 5.20 \ft Eph. 6:10, Mal. 2:7. \f*!
\v 21 Jun paap jana nai, Taike amikhan nimite paapi bonaise, titia amikhan Tai dwara Isor usorte dharmikta thaka hobole paribole nimite.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Etu nimite amikhan tai logote mili kene kaam kora khan pora apuni khan ke bhi utsah kori ase Isor laga anugraha ke misa-misi nalobi.
\v 2 Kilekoile Tai koise,
\q1 “Ami apnikhan ke ekta homoi te huni loise,
\q1 Aru poritran laga dinte ami apuni khan ke modot korise\f + \fr 6.2 \ft Isa 49.8. \f*.”
\m Sabi, etiya bhal homoi ase. Sabi, etiya poritran laga din ase.
\v 3 Amikhan kunke bhi girai dibole kaam kora nai, amikhan sewa kora bodnam nahobo nimite.
\v 4 Hoilebi, sob te amikhan nije ke Isor laga kaam kora manu khan ase koi kene dikhai thakibo; nijorke rukhabole parikena, dukh te, dorkar te, digdar te,
\v 5 mari kha-a te, bondhi ghor te, gondugol te, tan kaam te, ghuma bole napara rati khan te, bhuka thaka homoi te;
\v 6 sapha pora, gyaan pora, nijorke rukhabole para, Pobitro Atma pora, hosa laga morom pora,
\v 7 Hosa laga kotha pora, Isor laga takot pora; dyna hathte aru baya hathte dhormikta laga hathiar khan pora,
\v 8 Sonman aru sorom pora, bhal khobor aru biya khobor pora: thoga-baji nisena, aru hoilebi hosa te;
\v 9 Najana nisena, hoile bhi bhal pora jani thaka; mori juwa nisena, hoilebi sabi, jinda ase; mar kha-a nisena, kintu morai diya nai\f + \fr 6.9 \ft 1Cor. 4:9, Psa. 118:18. \f*;
\v 10 Mon dukh kora nisena, kintu hodai khushi pora thaka; dukhia nisena, kintu bisi khan ke dhuni bonaise; eku bhi nathaka nisena, kintu sob paikene ase.
\p 
\v 11 Oh Corinth laga manu khan, apnikhan usorte amikhan laga mukh khuli kene ase, amikhan laga mon bhi dangor khuli kene ase.
\v 12 Amikhan pora apnikhan ke dhuri bandhikena rakha nohoi, kintu apnikhan nijor laga morom bhabona pora he apnikhan bandhi kene ase.
\v 13 Etiya etu laga ekta bhal bodli kori bole nimite to- ami bacha khan ke kowa nisena- apnikhan bhi mon dangor khuli bhi.
\s1 Jivit Isor Laga Mondoli
\p 
\v 14 Apuni khan biswas nakora khan logote eke hoi kene namilibi. Kilekoile dhormikta te thaka khan aru niyom nathaka khan logot ki mili bole ase? Aru puhor to andhar logot ki mili bole paribo?
\v 15 Aru Khrista to Belial\f + \fr 6.15 \ft Saitan.\f* logote ki kotha milai kene rakhibo? Nohoile biswas kora jon pora abiswasi logote ki bhag ase?
\v 16 Aru Isor laga mondoli to murti khan logote ki kotha milai kene rakhise? Kilekoile amikhan jinda Isor laga mondoli ase jineka Isor pora koi dise;
\q1 “Ami taikhan bhitor te thakibo, aru taikhan bhitor te berabo;
\q1 Aru ami taikhan laga Isor hobo,
\q1 Aru taikhan ami laga manu khan hobo\f + \fr 6.16 \ft Lev. 26:12, Jer. 32:38, Eze. 37:27. \f*.”
\m 
\v 17 Etu nimite,
\q1 “Taikhan majot pora ulaikena Ahibi,
\q1 Aru apnikhan alag hobi,” Probhu koi ase,
\q1 “Aru niyom pora moila thaka saman na chubi,”
\q1 “Aru ami apnikhan ke mani lobo\f + \fr 6.17 \ft Isa. 52.11, Jer. 51:45. \f*.”
\q1 
\v 18 “Aru apnikhan laga Baba hobo,
\q1 Aru apnikhan ami laga chokra khan aru chukri khan hobo\f + \fr 6.18 \ft 2 Sam. 7:14, 1 Chr. 17:13, Isa. 43:6. Hos. 1:10 \f*,”
\m Sob pora Mohan Probhu pora koi ase.
\c 7
\nb 
\v 1 Moi bisi morom kora khan, etu kosom khan thaka nimite, amikhan laga mangso aru atma laga letera khan pora nije ke sapha kori lobo, aru Isor laga bhoi te thik pora pobitrota kori lobo.
\s1 Paul Laga Khushi
\p 
\v 2 Amikhan nimite jaga bonabi! Kilekoile amikhan kun manu ke bhi galti kora nai, amikhan kun manu ke bhi misa-misi kora nai, amikhan kun manu ke bhi thoga baji kora nai.
\v 3 Ami apuni khan ke golti janabole nimite etu kowa nohoi; kele koile ami poila pora koise, amikhan laga mon bhitor te apnikhan ase, aru eke logote he moribo aru jinda thakibo.
\v 4 Ami bhoi nakorikena apnikhan logote kotha koi ase, ami apnikhan laga naam untcha kori bole bisi ase: ami mon aram hoi kene ase, amikhan laga sob dukh aru digdar te ami bisi khushi paikena ase.
\p 
\v 5 Kilekoile, jitia amikhan Macedonia jagate ahise, amikhan bisi dukh te thakise. Aru sob phale digdar paise- bahar te lorai khan asele, aru bhitor te bhoi.
\v 6 Eneka hoile bhi Isor, jun mon chutu hoi kene thaka khan ke aram diye, Titus aha pora amikhan ke anondo dangor kori dise,
\v 7 Aru khali tai aha nimite he nohoi, kintu apnikhan pora taike mon dangor kori diya te amikhan bhi anondo hoise, aru moike lok kori bole itcha pora mon bhorta thaka, kandikena mon ghurai aha, moi logote milikena modot kori bole itcha thaka, eitu khan sob khobor huni kene moi arubi bisi khushi paise.
\v 8 Kilekoile moi laga ekta chithi pora apnikhan ke mon dukh kori bole dise, hoile bhi ami golti bhabona nai, -olop homoi nimite golti lagise, jitia moi dikhise apnikhan etu chithi nimite mon dukh hoise, khali ek ghanta nimite hoile bhi.-
\v 9 Etiya ami khushi ase, apnikhan mon dukh huwa nimite nohoi, hoilebi apnikhan mon dukh lagi kene paap pora mon ghura nimite. Kilekoile apuni khan ke bhal nimite mon dukh lagi bole dise, apnikhan mon ghura bole tak mon dukh hoise. Kilekoile, Isor laga itcha te apnikhan mon dukh hoise, aru etu nimite apnikhan to amikhan karone eku te nuksan nohobole nimite.
\v 10 Kilekoile Isor pora lagi thaka mon dukh to paap pora mon ghura bole diye juntu pora mon chinta nathaki kene poritran pai. Hoilebi etu prithibi laga mon dukh to mora he ane.
\v 11 Kilekoile sabi, juntu bhal nimite apuni khan ke Isor pora mon dukh kori bole dise, etu pora apnikhan bhitor te kiman kaam korise. Kiman mon bhorta huwa, kiman nijor nimite safai koribo dise, kiman khong, kiman bhoi, kiman mon pora lagi thaka bhabona, kiman biya laga bodla lobole mon laga bhabona! Eitu khan sob bhitor te apnikhan eku golti nathaka nijor pora dikhai dise.
\v 12 Etu nimite, ami apuni khan ke poila likha bhi, ami tai nimite likha nohoi jun golti korise, tai nimite bhi likha nohoi jun galti nimite dukh paise, hoilebi Isor age te apuni khan laga mon kiman bhorta ase etu apnikhan ke buja bole nimite hoise.
\v 13 Etu nimite apnikhan laga mon aram te amikhan bhi aram paise.
\p Amikhan aru bhi bisi mon aram pa-a to, Titus laga khushi nimite, kele koile apnikhan sob pora tai laga atma ke aru bhi notun takot kori dise.
\v 14 Kilekoile apnikhan nimite ami tai usorte kiba phutani korile bhi, ami sorom laga nai; hoilebi jineka amikhan apuni khan ke sob hosa khan koi dise, eneka amikhan laga phutani bhi, juntu ami Titus usorte korisile, etu hosa paise.
\v 15 Aru tai laga bhitor te apnikhan nimite aru bhi morom bisi hoise, apnikhan sob pora kotha mana nimite tai apuni khan ke bhabona kori thake, jineka bhoi aru kapi kene apnikhan taike mani loise.
\v 16 Etu nimite ami khushi ase kele koile sob te ami apnikhan uporte mon dangor kori bole pare.
\c 8
\s1 Mon Khuli Kena Daan Dibole Kotha
\p 
\v 1 Etu uporte, bhai khan, amikhan laga itcha ase apnikhan janibo Isor laga morom laga asis juntu Macedonia laga girja khan uporte dise,
\v 2 Kineka digdar laga porikha te taikhan bisi khushi pora thakise aru taikhan bisi dukhiya hoile bhi khuli kene di thakise.
\v 3 Kilekoile taikhan jiman parise eneka dise, ami nije jani ase, hoi, aru taikhan logot thaka pora bhi nijor khushi pora dise,
\v 4 Amikhan logote bisi morom-mangi kene prathana korise amikhan pobitro manu khan logote milikena kaam kora laga asis taikhan ke bhi punchibo nimite.
\v 5 Aru amikhan bhabona kora nisena nohoi, hoilebi poila taikhan nijorke Probhu logote dise, aru Isor laga monjur pora amikhanke bhi dise.
\v 6 Iman tak amikhan Titus nimite bhabona korise, jineka tai anugraha laga kaam shuru korise, eneka pora tai apnikhan bhitor te etu kaam pura kori bole.
\v 7 Etu nimite, jineka apuni khan sob jinis te bisi hoi kene ase, biswas te, kotha te, aru dimag te, aru hoshiar koi kene kaam khan mon diya te, aru amikhan nimite apnikhan laga morom te, sabi kineka pora apnikhan anugraha laga asis te bhi bisi hobole paribo.
\v 8 Ami hukum kotha koi diya nohoi, hoilebi dusra khan laga mon khula saikene, apnikhan laga sapha thaka morom ke porikha koribo nimite.
\v 9 Kilekoile apnikhan pora amikhan laga Probhu Jisu Khrista laga anugraha jani ase, jineka, Tai dhuni hoile bhi, apnikhan nimite tai dukhiya hoise, etu pora apnikhan dhuni hobole paribo nimite.
\v 10 Aru yate ami nije pora bujhai di ase: kele koile etu apnikhan nimite thik ase, kele koile apnikhan bisi itcha thakikena etu kaam to ek saal age te shuru korise.
\v 11 Etu nimite jineka kaam shuru kori bole itcha thakisele, eneka he apuni khan logot te ki ase, etu loi kene kaam to pura koribi.
\v 12 Kilekoile jodi ekjon tai laga ki ase etu pora inam dibole itcha thakile, etu he bhal ase, eku nathaka pora diya nohoikena.
\v 13 Ami laga motlob to apnikhan dukh paikena dusra khan hobi kuwa nohoi, kintu sob eke hobole nimite koi ase.
\v 14 Kilekoile etiya apnikhan logot bisi thaka pora taikhan ke dile, taikhan laga bisi pora apnikhan ke bhi dibole: titia ta te sob eke nisena hobo,
\v 15 Shastro te eneka likhi kene thaka nisena:
\q1 “Tai jun bisi joma korise tai logote bisi thaka nai,
\q1 Aru tai jun komti joma korise tai laga komti huwa nai\f + \fr 8.15 \ft Exo. 16:18.\f*.”
\s1 Titus Ke Stuti Kora
\m 
\v 16 Hoile bhi Isor ke dhanyavad di ase, jun Titus laga mon bhitor te apnikhan nimite bhabona kori bole dise.
\v 17 Kilekoile hosa pora tai amikhan laga kotha mani loise, hoile bhi bisi mon thaka nimite, tai laga nijor khushi pora apnikhan usorte jaise.
\v 18 Aru tai logote amikhan utu bhai ke pathaise, jun laga bhal naam sob girja khan te susamachar nimite ase;
\v 19 Aru khali etu he nohoi, hoilebi taike amikhan logote bera bole girja pora basi loise, Probhu\f + \fr 8.19 \ft Yate Probhu to Baba ke koi ase.\f* laga mohima karone aru amikhan laga itcha janai dibole aru ki anugraha kaam amikhan kori ase, etu kori bole dise.
\v 20 Amikhan hoshiar kora to, ki modot kaam amikhan pora korise, ta te kun pora bhi apatti nakoribole korise.
\v 21 Kelemane amikhan to Probhu age te he nohoikena manu khan sob age te bhi ki thik kaam ase, etu he korise.
\v 22 Aru amikhan laga bhai ke taikhan logot pathai ase, junke amikhan bisi bar porikha korise aru tai bisi kaam koribo mon thaka dikhise. Aru, etiya bhi tai apnikhan uporte biswas dangor thaka pora apnikhan logot kaam kori bole bisi itcha ase.
\v 23 Aru Titus to apnikhan nimite, amike modot kora aru ami laga sathi ase. Aru amikhan laga bhai khan to girja khan pora pathai diya manu khan ase, Khrista laga mohima nimite.
\v 24 Etu nimite, apnikhan pora girja khan ke apnikhan laga morom dikhai dibi, aru apnikhan laga naam te amikhan laga dangor kotha khan koi dibi.
\c 9
\s1 Jerusalem Laga Khristan Nimite Daan Joma Kora
\p 
\v 1 Aru pobitro manu khan\f + \fr 9.1 \ft Paul to Jerusalem te thaka Yehudi Khristan khan sobke likhi ase.\f* pora ki porisorja koribo lage etu hoile apuni khan ke ami likhi bole eku dorkar nai.
\v 2 Kilekoile ami apnikhan laga bhabona jani ase, juntu ami Macedonia te thaka khan ke mon dangor pora koi dise, ki Achaia to ek saal age pora taiyar ase, aru apnikhan laga itcha jui nisena joli thaka pora taikhan laga mon dangor kori dise.
\v 3 Kintu ami utu bhai khan ke pathaise, apnikhan nimite amikhan ki dangor kotha khan koise etu misa-misi nohobo nimite; etu karone ami koi diya nisena, apnikhan taiyar thakibi.
\v 4 Nohoile, jodi Macedonia manu kunba moi logote ahikena apnikhan taiyar nohoikena thaka dikhile, amikhan bisi sorom hobo- apnikhan nimite mon dangor pora koi diya to.
\v 5 Etu nimite moi etu dorkar ase bhabise ki bhai khan ke apuni khan logot pathaikena ki uphar apuni khan pora dibole kosom korise, etu ke taiyar rakhibole nimite. Eneka pora, etu uphar to asis nisena taiyar hobo, mon khushi pora diya, joborjosti pora nohoi.
\s1 Khushi Pora Diya Khan
\p 
\v 6 Hoilebi etu ami koi ase, Tai jun olop bijon phelabo olop he katibo, aru tai jun bisi bijon phelabo bisi katibo\f + \fr 9.6 \ft Pro. 11:24, 22:9.\f*.
\v 7 Jiman dibole ekjon pora mon bhitor te bhabi ase, eneka taike dibole dibi; biya paikena nohoi, nohoile dorkar nimite bhi nohoi, kele koile Isor khushi pora diya ke morom kore\f + \fr 9.7 \ft Deu. 18:10, Pro. 22:9, 11:25.\f*.
\v 8 Aru Isor pora apnikhan ke anugraha bisi dibole pare, tinehoile sob jinis khan te hodai bisi hoi kene, bisi pora bhal kaam kori bole paribo.
\v 9 Shastro te likhi kene thaka nisena:
\q1 “Tai sob uphale-ephale kori dise; Tai dukhiya khan ke dise
\q1 Tai laga dharmikta te thaka khan hodai nimite thakibo\f + \fr 9.9 \ft Psa. 112:9.\f*.”
\m 
\v 10 Etiya jun pora bijon phela manu ke bijon di ase aru roti khabole di ase, tai pora he phelai diya bijon bisi hobole di ase, aru apnikhan laga dharmikta laga phol khan aru bisi hobole di ase\f + \fr 9.10 \ft Isa. 55:10, Hos. 10:12. \f*;
\v 11 aru khushi pora diyi thaka te apnikhan ke arubi bisi hoi thaki kene, amikhan pora Isor ke dhanyavad dibo.
\v 12 Etu porisorja ke thik pora kori bole nimite pobitro manu khan ki lage etu he amikhan pora di thaki bole nohoi, hoilebi Isor ke bisi dhanyavad di thakibo lage.
\v 13 Aru jitia taikhan etu porisorja huwa dikhibo, titia taikhan Isor laga naam untcha koribo, apnikhan Khrista laga susamachar prochar kora nimite, aru apnikhan mon khuli kene taikhan aru sob manu ke diya nimite.
\v 14 Aru taikhan laga prathana apnikhan nimite thakibo, kele koile Isor laga dangor anugraha apnikhan logote bisi thaka nimite.
\v 15 Isor ke dhanyavad ase Tai laga kobole bhi napara daan nimite.
\c 10
\s1 Paul Laga Sewkai Kaam Bachai Luwa
\p 
\v 1 Etiya ami Paul nije Khrista laga niche aru norom hoi kene apnikhan ke anurodh kori ase - jun apnikhan laga majote thakile dorpok hoi kene thake, hoile bhi usorte nathakile ami bhoi nakori jai!
\v 2 Hoilebi ami apnikhan pora morom mangi ase, ami jitia usorte ahibo moi laga mon dangor kori kene bhoi nalagikena nathakilebi hobo, eneka hoile bhi ami bhabi ase kunba usorte ami biya paikena bhoi nakoribo, jun khan amikhanke bhabi ase jineka amikhan mangso hisab te berai thake.
\v 3 Kilekoile amikhan mangso bhitor te thaki kene beraile bhi, amikhan mangso hisab te lorai nakore.
\v 4 Kilekoile amikhan laga lorai laga hathiar khan gaw mangso nimite nohoi, hoilebi Isor laga takot pora takot dhuri kene thaka khan ke tanikena niche girai dibole laga ase.
\v 5 Misa-misi bhabona khan ke niche kori diye, aru sob dangor saman khan ke juntu nije ke uporte uthai thake Isor laga gyaan bhirodh te aru amikhan pora sob bhabona ke bandi kene Khrista laga kotha mani bole nimite kori diye.
\v 6 Aru amikhan taiyari kori kene ase, kotha namana khan ke bodla lobole, jitia apnikhan Khrista laga kotha mana to pura hoi jabo.
\v 7 Apnikhan samankhan laga bahar phine sai ase? Jodi kunba manu biswas kori ase tai Khrista laga ase koile, taike nije etu aru bhi bhabibole dibi, kele koile, jineka tai Khrista laga ase, eneka amikhan bhi Khrista laga ase.
\v 8 Kilekoile ami adhikar thaka laga phutani korile bhi etu amikhan laga kaam nimite ase, juntu Malik he amikhan ke dise hika bole nimite, aru biya kori bole nimite nohoi, ami sorom kori bole nalage,
\v 9 Ta te ami eneka dikhibole nalage jineka ami apuni khan ke chithi khan pora bhoi dikha bole kosis kori ase.
\v 10 Kilekoile, apuni kunba khan koi, “Tai laga chithi khan bhari thake aru joborjosti kore, kintu tai gaw pora to komjur ase, aru tai laga kotha eku daam nai.”
\v 11 Utuke eneka bhabibole dibi, jineka amikhan nijor gaw pora nathakile bhi chithi laga kotha te ase, eneka he amikhan kaam te bhi ase.
\v 12 Kilekoile amikhan nijorke utu kunba logote mila bole bhoi lage jun khan nijor laga kaam ke bhal koi thake. Taikhan kunkhan nijor majote kaam khan ujon kore, aru majote nijorke tulona kori thake, taikhan to dimag nai.
\v 13 Hoilebi amikhan, utu jinis khan nimite phutani nakoribo juntu amikhan nimite bisi hoijai, hoilebi Isor pora kiman tak kori bole dise etu hisab te he koribo, juntu apuni khan usorte bhi ponchise.
\v 14 Kilekoile amikhan ke dikena thaka kaam ke paar kori kene janai kitia amikhan apnikhan logote ahise, amikhan naha nohoi, kele koile Khrista laga susamachar nimite apnikhan usor tak ahise.
\v 15 Amikhan ke diya kaam paar kori kene dusra laga kaam te phutani kora nohoi, kintu, amikhan laga asha thaka to, jineka apuni khan laga biswas to dangor hoi thakibo, amikhan laga kaam apnikhan majote dangor hoi thakibo,
\v 16 apuni khan ke paar hoi kene napuncha jaga khan te susamachar laga kotha khan janai dibo nimite - aru dusra manu khan kaam kori kene rakha jaga khan te nijor hathte loi kene phutani nakoribo.
\q1 
\v 17 “Hoilebi tai jun naam untcha kori ase, taike Probhu bhitor te naam untcha kori bole dibi\f + \fr 10.17 \ft Jer 9.24, 1 Cor. 1.31\f*.”
\m 
\v 18 Kilekoile taike namanibo, jun nijor pora he nijor laga kaam bhal ase koi, hoilebi tai he hobo jun laga kaam Probhu pora bhal ase kobo.
\c 11
\s1 Paul Aru Misa Apostle Khan
\p 
\v 1 Murkho nisena hoilebi, Isor nimite amike olop dhorjo koribi, hoi apnikhan moike dhorjo kori ase!
\v 2 Kilekoile ami apnikhan uporte bhal nimite suku-juli ase: ami apnikhan ke ekjon mota logote milai dise, titia ami apuni khan ke ekjon pora sapha kumari maiki nisena Khrista usorte dibole paribo nimite.
\v 3 Kintu ami bhoi lage, jineka utu saph tai laga chalak kotha pora Eve ke thogaise, eneka pora he apnikhan laga Khrista te thaka sapha bhabona khan misa-misi hoi jabo\f + \fr 11.3 \ft Gen. 3:13, 1 The. 3:5.\f*.
\v 4 Kilekoile tai jun ahikena dusra Jisu laga prochar kore, juntu laga prochar amikhan kora nai, nohoile apnikhan dusra ekta atma paise, juntu apnikhan poila pa-a nai, nohoile dusra susamachar, juntu apnikhan poila mana nai, hobole pare apnikhan bhal para taike mani lobo!
\v 5 Kilekoile ami bhabona kori ase ami bhi “mohan apostle khan” pora chutu nohoi.
\v 6 Kintu ami kotha kobo najanile bhi, gyaan te moi eneka nohoi. Hoilebi apnikhan majote sob te sapha pora dikhai dibole parise.
\v 7 Na apnikhan laga naam untcha hobo nimite nije ke nomro kora to ami golti korise, kele koile moi Isor laga susamachar kotha eku daam noloikena janai dise?
\v 8 Moi dusra girja khan pora hajira loi kene dakaiti korise, apnikhan laga kaam te modot kori bole.
\v 9 Aru jitia ami apnikhan logote asele, aru dorkar thakile bhi ami kun pora bhi eku luwa nai. Kilekoile ami ki dorkar thakise, eitu khan sob Macedonia jaga pora aha biswasi bhai khan pora di dise. Sob te ami apnikhan usorte digdar hobole diya nai, aru ami etu he kori thakibo.
\v 10 Jineka Khrista laga hosa ami bhitor te ase, eneka he Achaia jaga phale tak te kun manu bhi ami phutani kori bole pora rukhabo na paribo.
\v 11 Ki nimite? Kilekoile ami apuni khan ke morom nakore? Isor jani ase moi apnikhan ke kiman morom kore!
\v 12 Hoilebi ami kori thaka to kori thakibo, titia kun pora nijorke taikhan bhi apostle ase eneka dikha bole kore aru amikhan logote borabar nisena kore, aru naam untcha kori bole kosis kore, taikhan logot pora moi etu hatai dibo.
\v 13 Kilekoile eneka khan misa-misi bhabobadi khan ase, thoga-baji laga kaam kora khan ase, nije ke Khrista laga apostle khan bona ase.
\v 14 Aru etu asurit nohoi; kele koile Saitan bhi tai nije ke ujala laga duth nisena bonaise.
\v 15 Etu nimite etu asurit nohoi jodi tai laga noukar khan nije ke dharmikta te thaka noukar khan nisena bonaile, jun khan bhi taikhan laga kaam hisab te khotom hobo.
\s1 Apostle Khan Nimite Paul Dukh Puwa
\p 
\v 16 Ami arubi koi ase: Kun manu bhi amike ekta murkho nabhabi bhi. Kintu eneka bhabile, ekta murkho nisena he amike mani lobi, tinehoile nijor nimite ami olop phutani kori bole paribo.
\v 17 Ami ki koi ase, etu ami Probhu laga niyom te kowa nohoi, hoilebi ekjon murkho nisena, etu phutani laga bhabona te koi ase.
\v 18 Bisi manu khan mangso te phutani kore, ami bhi mangso te phutani pora naam untcha koribo.
\v 19 Kilekoile apnikhan, gyaani huwa nimite, murkho khan ke khushi pora dhorjo kori loi.
\v 20 Aru manu pora apuni khan ke noukar bona, apuni khan ke khai diya, apuni khan pora loi diya, manu pora nijor naam untcha kora, apnikhan laga mukh te thapor mara, apnikhan to etu sob te dhorjo koriloi.
\v 21 Moi nijor sorom hoi kene koi ase, amikhan bhi eitu khan nimite bisi komjur hoise! Eneka hoilebi kunba naam untcha kori bole ase koile - ami murkho nisena koi ase- ami bhi naam untcha kori bole bhoi nai.
\v 22 Taikhan Ibrani jati khan ase? Ami bhi ase. Taikhan Israel jati ase? Ami bhi ase. Taikhan Abraham laga bijon ase? Ami bhi ase.
\v 23 Taikhan Khrista laga noukar khan ase? -Ami murkho nisena koi ase- ami taikhan pora bhi bisi ase: kaam khan ke bisi, bondhi ghor te bisi, mari kha-a te bisi, mora laga khatra te bisi.
\v 24 Pans bar ami “chalis bet laga mar khaise, ekta chari kene.”
\v 25 Tin bar amike lathi marise, ekbar pathor marise, tin bar ami pani jahaaj bhangai kene dukh paise, ek rati aru ek din ami pani bhitor te thakise.
\v 26 Bisi bar berai thakise, panikhan laga khatra pora bhoi, chor khan pora bhoi, ami laga nijor manu khan pora bhoi, paapi khan pora bhoi, sheher bhitor te bhoi, jongol te bhoi, samundar bhitor te bhoi, misa-misi bhai khan laga majote bhoi.
\v 27 Moi bisi dukh paikena raat bhar na ghumai kene, bhuk aru pyaas lagi kene, bisi bar upwas kori kene, thanda lagi kene aru lengta hoi kene bisi tan kaam khan kori ahise.
\v 28 Eitu khan logote, hodai din moi uporte sob girja khan laga chinta ahi thake.
\v 29 Kun komjur ase, aru ami komjur nohoi? Kun biswas pora giri jaise, aru ami juli thaka nohoi?
\v 30 Ami naam utcha lagi ase koile, ami utu jinis khan nimite naam untcha koribo juntu ami laga komjur khan ase.
\v 31 Amikhan laga Malik Jisu Khrista laga Isor aru Baba, jun hodai-hodai nimite asis paikene ase, jani ase ami misa kowa nohoi.
\p 
\v 32 Damascus te, raja Aretas laga niche thaka Governor to Damascus sheher te sipahi khan logote amike dhori bole nimite bisi bhabona kori kene rukhi thakise.
\v 33 Aru amike ekta tukri bhitor te rakhi kene pathor laga dewar laga ekta khirki pora amike niche kori dise, aru tai laga hath pora ami polaise.
\c 12
\s1 Paul Laga Darshan Aru Kata
\p 
\v 1 Naam utcha kori thaka ami nimite dorkar ase, kintu etu eku labh nai. Kintu ami Probhu laga darshan khan aru prokahit kora khan kobo.
\v 2 Choudah saal pora bisi, ami Khrista te thaka ekjon manu ke jani ase,- sharir te na sharir bahar, etu ami kobole napare; Isor jani ase- eneka ekjon tisra sorgote thakise.
\v 3 Ami eneka ekjon manu jani ase- sharir te na sharir bahar te ase, ami kobole napare, Isor jani ase-
\v 4 Taike kineka Paradise te loi jaise, aru bujhi bole napara kotha khan hunise, juntu manu kobole bhi mana ase.
\v 5 Eneka ekjon nimite ami naam untcha koribo. Hoilebi nijor laga naam untcha ami nakoribo, hoilebi ami laga biya khan nohoile.
\v 6 Kilekoile ami naam untcha kori bole mon hoilebi, ami murkho hobole nohoi, kele koile ami hosa kotha he kobo. Kintu moi etu pora nijorke rukhai thake, nohoile kunba manu ami kineka dikhi ase, nohoile amike kineka huni ase etu pora uporte bhabibo nadibole nimite.
\v 7 Aru utu bisi dangor kotha khan prokahit kora khan karone nijor laga bisi naam untcha nakoribo nimite, ami laga mangso bhitor te amike ekta kata dikene ase- Saitan laga khobor janai diya jon- amike mari thaki bole etu pora ami bisi phutani nohobo nimite.
\v 8 Etu nimite ami pora Probhu ke tin bar anurodh korise moi pora etu hatai dibi koi kene.
\v 9 Aru Tai amike koise, “Ami laga anugraha he tumi nimite kafi ase: kele koile ki komjur ase etu to Ami laga hokti pora he thik kori diye.” Etu nimite bisi khushi pora ami laga komjur khan nimite naam untcha koribo, tinehoile Khrista laga hokti ami uporte thakibo.
\v 10 Etu nimite kitia ami komjur hoijai, gali khai, digdar hoi, dukh kosto din lok pai, aru bisi mon dukh huwa homoi ahe, titia moi Khrista nimite khushi hobo: kele koile jitia ami komjur ase, titia ami logote takot ase.
\s1 Corinth Mondoli Karone Chinta
\p 
\v 11 Moi ekjon murkho hoise; apnikhan amike eneka kori bole dise: kele koile apnikhan pora moi bhal ase kobo lagisele. Kilekoile eku nohoile bhi ami “sob pora bhal apostle khan” laga pichete thaka nohoi.
\v 12 Hosa pora, sob te dhorjo kori kene, ekjon apostle laga chihna khan dikha bole nimite apnikhan majote kaam korise, asurit aru dangor kaam khan.
\v 13 Kilekoile, eneka hoise naki ami pora dusra girja khan ke chari kene apnikhan ke he biya pora cholai se, ami nijor apnikhan nimite ekta boja nisena nabona to chari kene? Etu galti nimite amike maph koribi.
\p 
\v 14 Sabi! Ami apnikhan logote tin bar ahibole taiyar ase; aru ami apnikhan ke digdar nadibo. Kilekoile ami apnikhan laga ki ase etu nalage, khali apnikhan ke he lage. Kilekoile bacha khan pora ama-baba khan nimite joma kori bole nalage, hoilebi ama-baba khan pora bacha khan karone joma kore.
\v 15 Aru ami bisi khushi pora kharcha koribo aru apnikhan laga atma khan nimite ami kharcha koribo. Jodi ami apnikhan ke bisi morom kore koile, apnikhan etu pora komti amike morom koribo?
\v 16 Hoilebi eneka hobole dile bhi, ami apnikhan ke digdar diya nai, kintu chalak thaka manu huwa pora, ami apnikhan ke galti adat te dhorise.
\v 17 Apnikhan ke kunba pathai kene ami labh uthaise, eneka moi korise?
\v 18 Ami Titus ke apnikhan logote jabole uksai se, aru tai logote ami ekjon bhai ke pathaise. Titus to apnikhan pora eku labh utha nai, na tai eneka korise? Amikhan ekta atma te berai thaka nohoi? Amikhan ekta rasta te he berai thake nohoi?
\p 
\v 19 Aru eneka bhabi ase naki apnikhan usorte amikhan nijorke safai di ase? Amikhan Khrista te thaki kene Isor naam te koi ase: amikhan etu sob kori thaka to, bisi morom thaka, apuni khan ke mojbut kori bole nimite ase.
\v 20 Kilekoile ami bhoi lage, hobole pare, jitia ami ahibo, apuni khan ke eneka napabo jineka ami bhabi ase, aru amike apnikhan pora jineka bhabona kora nai eneka pabo pare, hobole pare ta te jhagara khan, suku-jula, khong kora, mara-mari, chukuli, bodnam kora, phutani kora, gondugol khan hobo bhi pare.
\v 21 Aru hobole pare, jitia ami aru bhi ahibo, ami laga Isor amike apnikhan laga majote norom kori dibo, aru ami bisi nimite bisi mon-dukh koribo jun khan paap korise, aru bebichari kori ahise kintu mon to ghura aha nai, taikhan nimite moi mon dukh pora kandibo.
\c 13
\s1 Hekh Te Hoshiar Kotha
\p 
\v 1 Etiya ami apnikhan logote ahile etu tin bar hobo. “Sob kotha te, duijon nohoile tinjon pora sakhi korile he khara koribi.”
\v 2 Ami dusra bar aha homoi te hoshiar kotha koi dise, etiya ami apnikhan majote nai; hoile bhi kunkhan poila te paap kori thakise, aru dusra sob jon, jodi moi aru bhi taikhan logote ahile, ami kunke bhi nacharibo,
\v 3 Kilekoile apnikhan to Khrista ami dwara kotha koi ase na nai etu janibole bisari ase. Tai apnikhan phale komjur nohoi, hoilebi apnikhan majot te takot ase.
\v 4 Kilekoile Taike komjur hoi kene Cross te morai dise, hoilebi Tai Isor laga takot pora jinda ase. Kilekoile amikhan bhi Tai bhitor te komjur ase, hoilebi amikhan tai logote Isor laga takot pora apnikhan phale jinda thakibo.
\v 5 Apnikhan biswas bhitor te ase na nai, nijorke porikha koribi. Apnikhan nije ke nije pora porikha koribi. Na apnikhan bhitor te Jisu Khrista ase koi kene najane- apnikhan nijor pora porikha te gira nai koile?
\v 6 Hoilebi porikha kora homoi te, moi khan gira nai koi kene apnikhan janibole moi laga asha ase.
\v 7 Etiya ami Isor logot prathana kori ase apnikhan pora eku bhi biya nakoribole, amikhan porikha te jitise eneka dikha bole karone nohoi, hoilebi apnikhan juntu hosa ase etu he kori bole lage, amikhan porikha te gira nisena hoilebi.
\v 8 Kilekoile amikhan hosa ke biya paikena eku bhi kori bole napare, hoilebi hosa nimite he kore.
\v 9 Kilekoile amikhan khushi kore, jitia amikhan komjur ase, apnikhan logote takot ase. Aru amikhan etu bhi prathana kori ase: apnikhan ekdom thik hobo karone.
\v 10 Etu nimite ami nathakikena eitu khan likhi ase, hobole pare ami thakile ami laga adhikar kara pora nacholabo pare- utu adhikar pora juntu amike Malik dise, bona bole nimite, aru bhanga bole nimite nohoi.
\s1 Hekh Salam Kotha
\p 
\v 11 Hekh te, bhai khan, khushi kori thakibi! Nijorke thik koribi, mon dangor thakibi, ekta bhabona kori kene thakibi, shanti pora thakibi; aru morom laga aru shanti laga Isor apnikhan logote thakibo.
\v 12 Pobitro chuma pora ek-dusra ke salaam dibi.
\v 13 Sant-khan sob apunikhan ke salaam dise.
\v 14 Probhu Jisu Khrista laga anugraha, aru Isor laga morom, aru Pobitro Atma laga sangoti apnikhan sob logote thaki bole dibi. Amen.
